title: AIIMS Mangalagiri Jobs 2025 - Apply Online for 76 Senior Resident/ Senior Demonstrators Posts
description: The All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Mangalagiri, Andhra Pradesh (AIIMS Mangalagiri) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 76 Senior Resident/ Senior Demonstrators Jobs. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Post-graduation, MD/MS, DNB, M.Sc., and Ph.D. can apply for the AIIMS Mangalagiri Jobs 2025. The interested applicants can apply in ...
